T1  - Designing Meaningful Learning Situations In Management: A Contingency, Decision-Tree Approach
AU  - Randolph, W. Alan
AU  - Posner, Barry Z.
Y1  - 1979/07/01
PY  - 1979
DA  - 1979/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1979.4289136
